(252, 38, 0, 'Conferencia inaugural', '<p align="center" class="x_MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: 13px; text-align: center;">\n	<b><u><span lang="CA" style="font-size: 16pt; color: rgb(0, 32, 96);">Sessi&oacute; Inaugural del M&agrave;ster ICACS</span></u></b></p>\n<p align="center" class="x_MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: 13px; text-align: center;">\n	<span lang="CA" style="font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 32, 96);">Confer&egrave;ncia:<b>&nbsp;&quot;&iquest;Existe evidencia de que la MBE (Medicina basada en la evidencia) funciona en la pr&aacute;ctica?&rdquo;</b>&nbsp;a c&agrave;rrec del&nbsp;<b>Dr. JOS&Eacute; I. EMPARANZA</b>&nbsp;(Cap de la Unitat d&rsquo;Epidemiologia Cl&iacute;nica, Hospital Universitari de Donostia. Professor de Medicina Preventiva i Salut P&uacute;blica, Universitat del Pa&iacute;s Basc.)</span></p>\n<p align="center" class="x_MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: 13px; text-align: center;">\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p align="center" class="x_MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: 13px; text-align: center;">\n	<b><u><span lang="CA" style="font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 32, 96);">Dia, hora i lloc:</span></u></b></p>\n<p align="center" class="x_MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: 13px; text-align: center;">\n	<span lang="CA" style="font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 32, 96);">Data: dimecres,&nbsp;<b>4 d&rsquo;octubre de 2017 a les 15.30 h</b></span></p>\n<p align="center" class="x_MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, serif, EmojiFont; font-size: 13px; text-